Invocation Name: wes corwin comedy
des:
Wes Corwin has been declared the Best Comedian in Dallas and the Funniest Comedian in Texas (in 2018).

And now, he's an Amazon Alexa Skill! This skill is the best way to use your Amazon Alexa to listen to jokes, learn about upcoming shows and get inside the mind of comedian Wes Corwin.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
